**************************************************************************
** Section 1: IO Control
**************************************************************************
**
TITLE1
'TUPREP'

TITLE2
'W-O-14layer'


** Unit System
** FIELD, SI
INUNIT
FIELD


*WPRN   *WELL   *TIME    ** Frequencia de impressao no arq. saida .OUT
*WPRN   *GRID   0
*WPRN   *ITER   *BRIEF

*OUTPRN *WELL   *ALL     ** Informacoes a serem impressas arq.saida .OUT
*OUTPRN *RES    *ALL
*OUTPRN *TABLES *NONE
*OUTPRN *GRID   *NONE

*WSRF   *GRID   1        ** Frequencia de gravacao nos arq. .IRF e .MRF
*WSRF   *WELL   1

                                             ** Informacoes a serem gravadas nos
*OUTSRF *GRID *SW *SG *SO *PRES *DATUMPRES   ** arq. .IRF e .MRF
*OUTSRF *WELL *LAYER *ALL

**
****************************************************************************
** Section 2: Reservoir Description
**************************************************************************-
**
**Grid size
GRID CART 50 50 14

KDIR DOWN

**Grid block size in x-direction
DI CON 200 

**Grid block size in y-direction
DJ CON 200

**Grid block size in z-direction
DK CON 10

**Depth
DEPTH 1 1 1 4805

**Porosity
INCLUDE 'poro_base.inc'

**Net-to-gross ratio
NETGROSS CON 1.0

**Inactive grid blocks
NULL CON 1.0

**Permeability in x-direction
INCLUDE 'permx_base.inc'

**Permeability in y-direction
PERMJ  EQUALSI

**Permeability in z-direction
PERMK  EQUALSI  * 0.1

**
** Rock Compressibility
CPOR 0.00006103

** Rock Compressibility Pressure Reference
PRPOR 3408.205

**
**
****************************************************************************
** Section 3: Fluid Properties
****************************************************************************
**
MODEL BLACKOIL

** Reservoir Temperature
TRES 100.000

** PVT Table
PVT *BG 1
**    P            Rs           Bo            Bg       VisO   VisG    
**    (psia)    (SCF/STB)    (RB/STB)      (RB/STB)    (cP)   (cP)    
     14.70      0.000000     1.05           1.0000     2.20   .0125
  10014.70      1.00E-10     1.051          1.0000     2.20   .0125
**

** Oil Density
DENSITY OIL    56.930

** Water Density
DENSITY WATER  62.428

** Gas Density
DENSITY GAS     0.0516

** Oil Compressibility
CO    4.E-6

** Oil Viscosity Compressibility
CVO   0.0

** Water FVF
BWI   1.0042

** Water Compressibility
CW    3.744E-6

** Water Compressibility Pressure Reference
REFPW 3400.37

** Water Viscosity
VWI   0.5

** Water Viscosity Compressibility
CVW   0.0

**
****************************************************************************
** Section 4: Rock-Fluid Properties
****************************************************************************
**
ROCKFLUID
RPT 1

