0.500	0.20000	0.25000	0.000
0.550	0.25313	0.19141	0.000
0.600	0.31250	0.14063	0.000
0.650	0.37813	0.09766	0.000
0.700	0.45000	0.06250	0.000
0.750	0.52813	0.03516	0.000
0.800	0.61250	0.01563	0.000
0.900	0.80000	0.00000	0.000

SGT
** Sg 	Krg 	Krog 	Pcog
0.000	0.00000	1.00000	0.000
0.900	0.00001	0.00000	0.000

****************************************************************************
** Section 5: Initial Condition
****************************************************************************
**

INITIAL

VERTICAL DEPTH_AVE WATER_OIL EQUIL
** DATUM
DATUMDEPTH 4800.0
**
** Reference Depth
REFDEPTH 4800.0

** Initial Pressure
REFPRES 3800.00

** Water-Oil Contact Depth
DWOC 4990.0

** Bubble Pressure
PB CON 14.70
**
****************************************************************************
** Section 6: Numerical Settings
****************************************************************************
**
NUMERICAL
**

DTMIN          0.0001        ** Minimum Time step size

DTMAX         30.0           ** Maximum Time step size

MAXSTEPS      1000           ** Maximum Number of Time steps

NCUTS         10             ** Maximum Number of Time step cuts

                             ** Time step size control
NORM *PRESS   50.00          ** max. change in pressure   at a timestep
NORM *SATUR    0.05          ** max. change in saturation at a timestep

AIM STAB

